        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Leviticus 14:49",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", etc. When spun and dyed by the women, it was delivered in the state of yarn; and the weaving and embroidering was left to Aholiab and his assistants, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Exodus 35:25",
        "children": []
